data.title: Former Japanese PM Kaifu passes away
data.meta_description: Former Japanese PM Kaifu passes away-
data.text:
TOKYO, Jan. 14 (Xinhua) -- Former Japanese Prime Minister Toshiki Kaifu passed away this month, Japanese public broadcaster NHK reported Friday.

He was 91 years old.

After the Gulf War, the Japanese Self-Defense Force were deployed to the Gulf region to conduct minesweeping operations during Kaifu's term of office. â–
